<bibRefCitation id="EFA54B2BFFB4FF91FE54FF61FD016FE2" author="Kapur, A. P. &amp; Kripalani, M. B." box="[405,723,151,177]" pageId="17" pageNumber="516" pagination="183 - 221" refId="ref10730" refString="Kapur, A. P. &amp; Kripalani, M. B. (1963) The mayflies (Ephemeroptera) from the north - western Himalaya. Records of the Indian Museum, 59, 183 - 221." type="journal article" year="1963">Kapur &amp; Kripalani, 1963</bibRefCitation>
